Ep.04 — Retrieving Data & Filtering Results

📺 Watch this episode: [YouTube Link]
⬅️ Previous: [Ep.03 — Data Manipulation] ( https://youtu.be/H5AnKGSS1Vc?si=N7TapB_zWRhJqO-7 )


## 📌 What You Will Learn

- SELECT — fetch specific columns from a table
- Column aliases — rename output columns cleanly
- ORDER BY — sort results ascending or descending
- LIMIT & OFFSET — control how many rows you get
- WHERE — filter rows by condition
- Comparison operators — =, !=, >, <, >=, <=
- AND, OR, NOT — combine multiple conditions
- BETWEEN — range filter (inclusive)
- IN — match against a list of values
- LIKE — pattern matching with % and _
- IS NULL / IS NOT NULL — handle missing values
- DISTINCT — remove duplicate values from output

